line_1: Ye vivid tints of Persia's looms,
The costly Pride of Persian Looms,
line_2: And Guido's Paintings, grace his Rooms.

line_1: Silkworms and spiders at their looms,
line_2: And ants that hoard ere winter comes;

line_1: Midst pois'nous smokes and steams, and rattling looms;
line_2: Her poring thousands stows in breathless rooms,
Fine was the texture, such as comes
